commit.message:
Add PICOJSON_NOEXCEPT macro to switch between empty throw() and noexcept.
Use noexcept by default if RVALUE_REFERENCES are being used.
GCCs rules for implicit move constructor deletion inferrence don't seem to
treat throw() and noexcept equivalently.
fix -Wcatch-value warnings with gcc8
